<subSubSection pageId="199" pageNumber="477" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="199.[106,1313,1447,1946]" pageId="199" pageNumber="477">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[108,242,1636,1669]" pageId="199" pageNumber="477">Breeding.</emphasis>
Female Smoky Grass Mice had embryos in October-November, and nonpregnant females were caught in June-July and September.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
